74. EXT. DESERT. ABANDONED VILLAGE- NIGHT
In the open shot under the moonlight, Najmeh, Rezvan, and Sana 
are running in the desert towards the abandoned village. 
Suddenly, two points of light (Iman's car) come toward them from 
the orchard. Near the village, Rezvan notices Iman's car. She 
shouts.
REZVAN
Run in different directions!
    

p. 125
Share

      Najmeh, Rezvan, and Sana enter the ruins of the village, each in
a different direction.
After a few moments, Iman's car stops in front of the village 
amidst the dust raised by the tires. He gets out of the car and 
enters the village. Iman is searching for Sana, Rezvan, and 
Najmeh.
Rezvan, Sana, and Najmeh are searching for a shelter to stay out 
of Iman's sight.
75. EXT. ABANDONED VILLAGE- DAWN TO SUNRISE (SUN RISES AND 
LIGHTS UP THE SKY DURING THIS SCENE)
After searching for a while, Iman hears a voice from the roof of 
the room he is in. He quietly climbs up the roof from the worn￾out brick walls and fragile stairs. Najmeh has taken refuge in a 
